  <link href="Reference_CommandsTab.dita" class="- topic/link " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/huviz/HuViz_Concept.dita" xtrc="link:2;12:43" type="concept"><?ditaot gentext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext ">Using the Commands Tab</linktext><?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">Working directly in the Graph using the "drag and drop" technique involves fewer steps. However, working from the Commands Tab has multiple benefits.<image placement="break" href="https://cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A3550c158-99dd-49a7-9313-72694d3672b6/datastream/OBJ/view" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/huviz/Reference_CommandsTab.dita" xtrc="image:1;5:332"/></desc></link>
